15 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
16 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY 63 O.S. 2021, Section 5030.1, is
17 amended to read as follows:
18 Section 5030.1. A. There is hereby created within the Oklahoma
19 Health Care Authority the Medicaid Drug Utilization Review Board,
20 which shall be responsible for the development, implementation and
21 assessment of retrospective and prospective drug utilization
22 programs under the direction of the Authority.
